replies.body:
I already wrote Cass's strategy into a powershell command to keep things simple:

function ComplicatedDamageScript {
    If($Target.poisoned -eq $True) {return "E"}
    Else {return "Q"}
}

Now bind that to a random key on your keyboard .... heck to your entire keyboard ... and slap it repeatedly ... you have now mastered the new champion damage mechanics.  If you don't want to use this script you can do it manually, that's what Riot apparently refers to as a *meaningful choice* now.
